1
00:00:03,103 --> 00:00:04,104
Will you kneel?

2
00:00:04,671 --> 00:00:06,551
I only kneel to the
emperor of the Xing dynasty.

3
00:00:06,840 --> 00:00:08,675
You've been abandoned by your family.

4
00:00:08,908 --> 00:00:10,443
Do you even know what a hostage is?

5
00:00:10,744 --> 00:00:12,479
If you dare to anger me again,

6
00:00:12,846 --> 00:00:14,681
I'll make you wish you were dead.

7
00:00:16,516 --> 00:00:17,684
Kill me,

8
00:00:18,151 --> 00:00:20,253
and my brothers will
send troops to attack you.

9
00:00:20,987 --> 00:00:22,598
Your father the emperor
won't spare you either.

10
00:00:22,622 --> 00:00:23,622
You...

11
00:00:27,360 --> 00:00:28,360
Crown Brother,

12
00:00:28,395 --> 00:00:30,497
I've heard this kid is extremely brutal.

13
00:00:30,764 --> 00:00:32,742
He killed the White-Eyed
Wolf King when he was nine.

14
00:00:32,766 --> 00:00:33,133
What do you think?

15
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:35,201
Will he secretly take revenge on us?

16
00:00:35,468 --> 00:00:36,002
Yeah,

17
00:00:36,202 --> 00:00:37,202
Crown Brother,

18
00:00:37,570 --> 00:00:39,439
His eyes look abnormal.

19
00:00:39,873 --> 00:00:41,650
Let's just teach him a
lesson and be done with it.

20
00:00:41,674 --> 00:00:43,309
If we really kill the hostage,

21
00:00:43,383 --> 00:00:46,116
Father the emperor will
definitely punish us if he finds out.

22
00:00:49,616 --> 00:00:51,117
Let's go, let's go.

23
00:00:54,020 --> 00:00:55,020
Go.

24
00:01:07,664 --> 00:01:09,967
You're the prince from the grasslands.

25
00:01:18,344 --> 00:01:19,989
All you Central Plains people are the same.

26
00:01:20,013 --> 00:01:21,815
Stop putting on an act.

27
00:01:29,055 --> 00:01:30,055
Crown Brother told you to change into

28
00:01:30,056 --> 00:01:31,191
our Central Plains clothes,

29
00:01:31,558 --> 00:01:32,798
and you actually disobeyed him.

30
00:01:32,859 --> 00:01:33,939
You really are a barbarian.

31
00:01:34,060 --> 00:01:35,700
You can't even understand human language.

32
00:02:04,257 --> 00:02:05,257
Come on,

33
00:02:07,060 --> 00:02:08,060
hurry up and take it.

34
00:02:38,150 --> 00:02:40,878
"Pei Yanzhi"

35
00:03:45,024 --> 00:03:46,024
That's not fair.

36
00:03:46,492 --> 00:03:47,492
You know martial arts.

37
00:03:59,272 --> 00:04:00,272
A Qi,

38
00:04:00,907 --> 00:04:02,307
do you want to learn swordsmanship?

39
00:04:03,076 --> 00:04:04,116
Practicing martial arts...

40
00:04:05,144 --> 00:04:06,479
Ever since I was seven

41
00:04:07,714 --> 00:04:09,274
and got injured at the training ground,

42
00:04:09,782 --> 00:04:11,982
my mother has never let
me practice martial arts again.

43
00:04:14,654 --> 00:04:15,654
I'll secretly teach you.

44
00:04:15,788 --> 00:04:17,099
We won't go to the training ground.

45
00:04:17,123 --> 00:04:18,123
Don't tell anyone else.

46
00:04:26,266 --> 00:04:27,934
This sword tassel is quite unique.

47
00:04:34,874 --> 00:04:35,874
Grip it tightly,

48
00:04:37,510 --> 00:04:38,510
and thrust it out.

49
00:07:19,105 --> 00:07:19,605
It's boring.

50
00:07:19,639 --> 00:07:20,719
I'm not practicing anymore.

51
00:07:21,007 --> 00:07:22,007
A Qi,

52
00:07:26,913 --> 00:07:28,047
I was just kidding.

53
00:07:28,893 --> 00:07:29,582
Yanzhi,

54
00:07:29,849 --> 00:07:30,950
you're so skilled.

55
00:07:31,551 --> 00:07:32,561
No wonder your uncle sent you

56
00:07:32,585 --> 00:07:34,053
to Daxing as a hostage.

57
00:07:35,388 --> 00:07:37,089
If you had stayed in the grasslands,

58
00:07:37,723 --> 00:07:40,193
you would definitely have
become a great Khan.

59
00:07:42,128 --> 00:07:43,162
Sacrificing myself

60
00:07:44,030 --> 00:07:45,750
to ensure the safety of my tribe and family

61
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:48,534
is more important to me

62
00:07:49,268 --> 00:07:50,603
than becoming a great Khan.

63
00:07:53,005 --> 00:07:54,005
Let's go.

64
00:07:59,998 --> 00:08:02,878
Yin Qi has never come on the autumn
hunt with Emperor Father before.

65
00:08:03,182 --> 00:08:05,262
This time, he actually
brought them, mother and son.

66
00:08:07,253 --> 00:08:09,555
The emperor dotes
greatly on the Crown Prince.

67
00:08:10,189 --> 00:08:12,058
But it seems that the
position of Crown Prince

68
00:08:12,325 --> 00:08:13,659
is not within easy reach

69
00:08:14,427 --> 00:08:16,162
for the Crown Prince.

70
00:08:18,264 --> 00:08:19,424
How dare you speak ill of me,

71
00:08:19,932 --> 00:08:21,267
the Daxing royal family!

72
00:08:22,001 --> 00:08:23,001
Do you know

73
00:08:23,536 --> 00:08:24,804
I could crush you to death

74
00:08:25,605 --> 00:08:28,007
as easily as crushing an ant?

75
00:08:30,409 --> 00:08:32,169
It's not that I'm
speaking ill of the court,

76
00:08:33,212 --> 00:08:34,692
but rather that Your Highness assumes

77
00:08:35,448 --> 00:08:37,928
that the position of Crown
Prince is easily within your grasp,

78
00:08:39,185 --> 00:08:40,620
while I'm just stating the truth.

79
00:08:41,988 --> 00:08:42,988
You...

80
00:08:48,294 --> 00:08:49,534
Your Highness is a smart person

81
00:08:50,263 --> 00:08:51,263
and should know

82
00:08:51,631 --> 00:08:53,065
that if I become your enemy,

83
00:08:53,599 --> 00:08:54,934
it will be of no benefit to you.

84
00:08:56,435 --> 00:08:57,637
But if I say

85
00:08:58,137 --> 00:08:59,305
that I can help Your Highness

86
00:08:59,772 --> 00:09:00,940
obtain what you desire,

87
00:09:02,642 --> 00:09:04,162
would Your Highness be willing to try?

88
00:09:10,449 --> 00:09:11,449
What makes you think

89
00:09:12,151 --> 00:09:13,286
I should believe you?

90
00:09:13,819 --> 00:09:15,421
Su He is willing to listen to you

91
00:09:15,988 --> 00:09:17,189
and work for me.

92
00:09:17,723 --> 00:09:19,483
Su He is a person who
values profit greatly.

93
00:09:20,246 --> 00:09:21,657
If he forms an alliance with Your Highness,

94
00:09:21,681 --> 00:09:23,350
it will bring him great benefits.

95
00:09:23,782 --> 00:09:24,782
For him,

96
00:09:24,897 --> 00:09:26,065
why wouldn't he do it?

97
00:09:29,068 --> 00:09:30,503
According to what you're saying,

98
00:09:30,836 --> 00:09:33,372
I can form an alliance with Su He myself.

99
00:09:33,839 --> 00:09:34,839
What use are you then?

100
00:09:36,609 --> 00:09:37,877
Because I'm a hostage,

101
00:09:38,811 --> 00:09:41,514
so I'm the only one

102
00:09:41,801 --> 00:09:44,033
who can open Su He's heart.

103
00:09:44,884 --> 00:09:45,985
In that case,

104
00:09:47,053 --> 00:09:49,355
what makes you think

105
00:09:49,522 --> 00:09:50,962
I should believe that you're sincere

106
00:09:50,990 --> 00:09:52,925
in helping me ascend to the throne?

107
00:09:55,795 --> 00:09:56,796
If this succeeds,

108
00:09:57,964 --> 00:09:59,284
I would like to ask Your Highness

109
00:09:59,465 --> 00:10:00,633
for one thing.

110
00:10:08,407 --> 00:10:09,842
Greetings, Fifth Prince.

111
00:10:09,976 --> 00:10:11,410
Fifth Prince, please calm down.

112
00:10:11,644 --> 00:10:13,846
The Crown Prince is
talking with the young prince

113
00:10:14,180 --> 00:10:15,180
right now.

114
00:10:16,849 --> 00:10:17,849
Who are you?

115
00:10:18,651 --> 00:10:21,320
I think I've seen you before.

116
00:10:21,821 --> 00:10:24,357
I was originally an opera performer.

117
00:10:24,924 --> 00:10:26,993
The Crown Prince
appreciated my performances

118
00:10:27,259 --> 00:10:29,128
and said he liked listening to me sing,

119
00:10:30,329 --> 00:10:32,998
so he allowed me to enter the palace

120
00:10:32,999 --> 00:10:34,400
and stay by his side.

121
00:10:34,667 --> 00:10:36,202
I never knew

122
00:10:36,802 --> 00:10:38,904
that my Crown Brother
liked listening to operas.

123
00:10:39,939 --> 00:10:40,939
Then tell me,

124
00:10:41,340 --> 00:10:43,843
what does my Crown
Brother usually like to listen to?

125
00:10:44,744 --> 00:10:45,744
Well...

126
00:10:47,546 --> 00:10:49,615
Has Fifth Prince never heard that

127
00:10:49,782 --> 00:10:52,652
everyone at our Yunshang
Pavilion is skilled at singing operas?

128
00:10:52,985 --> 00:10:54,320
If Fifth Prince likes it,

129
00:10:54,353 --> 00:10:56,098
then I can bring a clever
and charming person

130
00:10:56,122 --> 00:10:57,523
from Yunshang Pavilion tomorrow

131
00:10:57,590 --> 00:10:59,058
to serve Fifth Prince.

132
00:11:00,593 --> 00:11:01,694
Yunshang Pavilion.

133
00:11:03,195 --> 00:11:05,698
Fifth Prince looks so innocent,

134
00:11:05,931 --> 00:11:06,931
it's really tempting.

135
00:11:08,567 --> 00:11:09,769
Could it be that

136
00:11:09,935 --> 00:11:11,537
Fifth Prince likes

137
00:11:11,937 --> 00:11:14,607
the young prince in the tent?

138
00:11:16,442 --> 00:11:18,778
So Fifth Prince has a taste for that.

139
00:11:18,978 --> 00:11:22,014
Then I can't help you with that.

140
00:11:52,278 --> 00:11:53,512
Good Yanzhi,

141
00:11:54,046 --> 00:11:55,915
let me rest for a couple of days.

142
00:11:57,450 --> 00:11:58,560
I'm destined to be an idle prince

143
00:11:58,584 --> 00:12:00,019
for the rest of my life.

144
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:01,921
Besides,

145
00:12:02,088 --> 00:12:03,248
learning so much martial arts

146
00:12:03,456 --> 00:12:04,924
won't do me any good.

147
00:12:05,357 --> 00:12:06,717
You have a long life ahead of you.

148
00:12:06,892 --> 00:12:08,772
How do you know what
will happen in the future?

149
00:12:10,563 --> 00:12:12,431
I can't change the fact that I'm a prince.

150
00:12:12,731 --> 00:12:13,731
Could it be that

151
00:12:14,463 --> 00:12:16,068
I can go settle in Jiangnan?

152
00:12:16,535 --> 00:12:17,535
Of course,

153
00:12:20,372 --> 00:12:21,407
our fates

154
00:12:23,275 --> 00:12:25,377
are like kites being pulled in the sky,

155
00:12:27,913 --> 00:12:29,348
but I still want to be the one

156
00:12:29,915 --> 00:12:31,250
holding the kite string.

157
00:12:50,069 --> 00:12:51,070
A Qi,

158
00:12:51,930 --> 00:12:54,342
The royal city is full of
intrigues and schemes.

159
00:12:56,308 --> 00:12:58,010
The only thing I can do is

160
00:12:58,844 --> 00:13:00,546
do my utmost to protect you

161
00:13:01,647 --> 00:13:03,649
and to help you break
free from the shackles.

162
00:13:04,683 --> 00:13:06,786
Protecting the light in my life.

163
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:32,000
"Journey With You"

164
00:14:33,163 --> 00:14:35,137
(Episode 3)

165
00:14:40,579 --> 00:14:41,579
A Qi,

166
00:14:42,181 --> 00:14:43,249
why are you here?

167
00:14:47,119 --> 00:14:48,359
You must be worried about Heshu

168
00:14:49,989 --> 00:14:51,833
and came to look for her to go
back to the palace together, right?

169
00:14:51,857 --> 00:14:52,857
Heshu...

170
00:14:53,145 --> 00:14:54,947
She's probably having
too much fun somewhere

171
00:14:55,194 --> 00:14:56,671
and forgot the time
to return to the palace.

172
00:14:56,695 --> 00:14:57,596
But don't worry,

173
00:14:57,621 --> 00:14:58,522
I told Duan Yi.

174
00:14:58,597 --> 00:14:59,632
At this point,

175
00:15:00,566 --> 00:15:01,806
are you still going to hide it?

176
00:15:15,047 --> 00:15:16,047
Yanzhi,

177
00:15:16,582 --> 00:15:18,250
I'll give you a chance to explain.

178
00:15:18,717 --> 00:15:20,052
Why did you do this?

179
00:15:21,253 --> 00:15:22,521
Since you already know,

180
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:28,840
then there's nothing to do.

181
00:15:33,666 --> 00:15:34,786
You've known for a long time

182
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:37,520
for what reason Emperor Father
called me to the imperial study.

183
00:15:38,237 --> 00:15:41,307
All these years, you've
been taking advantage of me.

184
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:42,201
Of course not.

185
00:15:42,226 --> 00:15:43,226
I...

186
00:15:46,912 --> 00:15:47,912
Anyway,

187
00:15:48,580 --> 00:15:50,620
the less you know about
some things, the better.

188
00:15:53,852 --> 00:15:55,363
Su He and Yin Zhou have formed an alliance,

189
00:15:55,387 --> 00:15:56,867
and you're being threatened by Su He,

190
00:15:57,089 --> 00:15:57,923
so that's why you're working for him.

191
00:15:57,924 --> 00:15:58,957
Is that right?

192
00:15:59,625 --> 00:16:00,769
How did you two get involved?

193
00:16:00,793 --> 00:16:01,760
Tell me the truth.

194
00:16:01,794 --> 00:16:02,661
Tell me quickly,

195
00:16:02,662 --> 00:16:04,295
so I can find a way to
help you get out of it.

196
00:16:04,296 --> 00:16:05,497
Has Your Highness forgotten

197
00:16:06,231 --> 00:16:07,742
that I'm the prince of the Talhan tribe,

198
00:16:07,766 --> 00:16:09,406
not a subject of your father the emperor?

199
00:16:11,337 --> 00:16:12,438
I'm working for my people.

200
00:16:13,072 --> 00:16:14,072
What's wrong with that?

201
00:16:18,210 --> 00:16:19,611
I used to think

202
00:16:20,145 --> 00:16:21,145
that we were the ones

203
00:16:21,647 --> 00:16:23,682
who understood each
other best in this world.

204
00:16:24,950 --> 00:16:25,990
Now, all I want to know is

205
00:16:26,992 --> 00:16:29,454
the Yanzhi who secretly helped
my mother return to Jiangnan

206
00:16:29,782 --> 00:16:32,241
and the Feng Sui before me now
who aids the wicked...

207
00:16:33,632 --> 00:16:35,906
Which one is the real you?

208
00:16:37,863 --> 00:16:39,463
Then I also want to ask Your Highness...

209
00:16:41,567 --> 00:16:43,168
you used the matter of Concubine Chen

210
00:16:43,669 --> 00:16:44,669
to test me,

211
00:16:45,804 --> 00:16:47,039
and investigated me secretly.

212
00:16:48,073 --> 00:16:49,608
What am I in your eyes?

213
00:16:51,110 --> 00:16:52,110
A

214
00:16:54,213 --> 00:16:56,014
Hostage who might betray you at any time,

215
00:16:58,784 --> 00:17:00,384
or the family member you claim me to be?

216
00:17:00,619 --> 00:17:01,619
At least,

217
00:17:03,689 --> 00:17:05,209
I have a clear conscience towards you.

218
00:17:06,091 --> 00:17:07,091
And you?

219
00:17:08,260 --> 00:17:10,062
What secrets are you hiding?

220
00:17:14,433 --> 00:17:15,501
I took our friendship

221
00:17:15,534 --> 00:17:16,635
too seriously,

222
00:17:18,203 --> 00:17:19,203
But I forgot

223
00:17:20,339 --> 00:17:21,673
that you have another identity.

224
00:17:32,651 --> 00:17:33,691
I hope that in the future,

225
00:17:33,893 --> 00:17:35,427
when we face each other with swords,

226
00:17:37,056 --> 00:17:38,323
you can still say

227
00:17:39,491 --> 00:17:40,492
with a clear conscience

228
00:17:41,059 --> 00:17:42,059
these four words.

229
00:18:05,250 --> 00:18:06,351
I didn't expect that A Qi

230
00:18:06,785 --> 00:18:08,253
already knows so much.

231
00:18:09,755 --> 00:18:10,422
Now that the Fifth Prince

232
00:18:10,423 --> 00:18:11,690
has discovered this place,

233
00:18:12,191 --> 00:18:13,425
In the future, he will surely

234
00:18:13,759 --> 00:18:15,227
try to investigate our actions.

235
00:18:15,994 --> 00:18:16,994
It doesn't matter.

236
00:18:17,596 --> 00:18:18,596
The real secret letters

237
00:18:18,997 --> 00:18:20,032
are sent by messengers.

238
00:18:21,333 --> 00:18:22,333
It's just that

239
00:18:24,136 --> 00:18:25,776
the relationship between him and Yin Zhou

240
00:18:26,371 --> 00:18:27,839
can never return to the previous state

241
00:18:27,840 --> 00:18:29,107
of surface-level calmness.

242
00:18:32,344 --> 00:18:33,344
Go and find out

243
00:18:33,745 --> 00:18:34,880
how A Qi discovered

244
00:18:35,447 --> 00:18:37,459
that we were sending messages
in the Piaoxiang Pavilion.

245
00:18:37,483 --> 00:18:39,094
Yes. My lord.

246
00:18:51,430 --> 00:18:52,430
Your Highness,

247
00:18:53,966 --> 00:18:54,966
it is said that

248
00:18:55,167 --> 00:18:57,236
the things you wanted Yin Qi to know

249
00:18:57,436 --> 00:18:59,838
he now knows it all.

250
00:19:00,639 --> 00:19:02,908
But it seems that Yin Qi

251
00:19:03,142 --> 00:19:04,376
wants to protect Pei Yanzhi.

252
00:19:05,130 --> 00:19:09,681
I didn't expect that their
relationship is so good.

253
00:19:11,483 --> 00:19:13,318
Since Yin Qi is so reluctant,

254
00:19:14,653 --> 00:19:15,988
then I will

255
00:19:17,089 --> 00:19:18,090
give him another push.

256
00:19:19,224 --> 00:19:20,224
Yes.

257
00:19:25,230 --> 00:19:26,230
Your Highness,

258
00:19:26,598 --> 00:19:29,134
Every time Fu An reports
news about that person,

259
00:19:29,868 --> 00:19:31,069
you are always so eager.

260
00:19:31,570 --> 00:19:33,605
I don't know whether
you care about the news

261
00:19:33,839 --> 00:19:35,274
or the person.

262
00:19:37,409 --> 00:19:38,409
Your Highness,

263
00:19:38,844 --> 00:19:40,312
You are so biased.

264
00:19:48,153 --> 00:19:50,289
Whether it's you or him,

265
00:19:51,557 --> 00:19:52,858
to me,

266
00:19:53,792 --> 00:19:54,792
it's all the same.

267
00:20:09,241 --> 00:20:10,241
Your Highness,

268
00:20:10,742 --> 00:20:12,620
The matter concerning the young
master is of great importance.

269
00:20:12,644 --> 00:20:14,644
Are you really going to
keep this matter a secret?

270
00:20:15,581 --> 00:20:16,615
Now it seems that

271
00:20:16,882 --> 00:20:18,562
the person behind the Lotus Merchant Group

272
00:20:18,884 --> 00:20:19,884
is also the young master.

273
00:20:21,286 --> 00:20:22,286
Your Highness,

274
00:20:22,988 --> 00:20:25,948
The Piaoxiang Pavilion has been
established in the capital for many years.

275
00:20:26,191 --> 00:20:28,392
I'm afraid the young
master has been planning

276
00:20:28,393 --> 00:20:30,113
since the first day he entered the capital.

277
00:20:31,129 --> 00:20:32,129
Your Highness.

278
00:20:33,131 --> 00:20:34,131
Your Highness...!

279
00:20:39,905 --> 00:20:40,905
I know.

280
00:20:41,440 --> 00:20:42,040
This matter,

281
00:20:42,240 --> 00:20:43,520
no one is allowed to mention it.

282
00:20:44,309 --> 00:20:45,611
I need time to think it over.

283
00:20:48,747 --> 00:20:49,747
You may all leave now.

284
00:20:58,136 --> 00:20:59,538
You, the busy young lord,

285
00:20:59,725 --> 00:21:01,365
how come you have time to visit me today?

286
00:21:05,764 --> 00:21:08,804
Are you planning to keep talking to
me in such a sarcastic tone all the time?

287
00:21:14,039 --> 00:21:15,039
Unless

288
00:21:15,641 --> 00:21:17,276
you tell me

289
00:21:17,476 --> 00:21:18,516
everything I want to know.

290
00:21:24,049 --> 00:21:25,409
I know you're willing to trust me.

291
00:21:25,784 --> 00:21:26,285
A Qi,

292
00:21:26,652 --> 00:21:27,652
listen to me.

293
00:21:27,953 --> 00:21:29,713
Don't get involved in
court affairs anymore.

294
00:21:29,821 --> 00:21:30,822
I won't harm you.

295
00:21:31,356 --> 00:21:32,858
I know you won't harm me,

296
00:21:33,692 --> 00:21:34,692
but only by knowing

297
00:21:35,060 --> 00:21:36,561
what you've done behind my back

298
00:21:36,862 --> 00:21:39,464
can I find a way to stop
you from going too far.

299
00:21:42,601 --> 00:21:43,601
A Qi,

300
00:21:44,169 --> 00:21:45,169
Do you know

301
00:21:45,470 --> 00:21:46,550
that the Piaoxiang Pavilion

302
00:21:47,539 --> 00:21:49,579
was a ploy deliberately revealed
to you by Yin Zhou?

303
00:21:55,681 --> 00:21:56,681
I have indeed

304
00:21:57,616 --> 00:21:58,856
been sending messages to Su He,

305
00:22:00,152 --> 00:22:01,152
but those

306
00:22:01,820 --> 00:22:03,989
were just common knowledge
in the court.

307
00:22:04,990 --> 00:22:05,990
Over the years,

308
00:22:06,210 --> 00:22:08,690
I've tried my best to balance
the interests of various tribes.

309
00:22:08,760 --> 00:22:10,628
The Piaoxiang Pavilion
is just a place

310
00:22:10,629 --> 00:22:12,349
for my intelligence network in the capital.

311
00:22:13,158 --> 00:22:14,158
So that's how it is.

312
00:22:16,775 --> 00:22:17,775
In the past,

313
00:22:18,336 --> 00:22:19,866
we spent every day together,

314
00:22:20,732 --> 00:22:22,033
yet I never realized

315
00:22:22,888 --> 00:22:24,968
you had laid such a grand
chessboard behind my back.

316
00:22:25,514 --> 00:22:27,554
Yin Zhou deliberately
leaked the information to you

317
00:22:27,579 --> 00:22:29,019
in an attempt to interfere with you.

318
00:22:30,248 --> 00:22:32,128
My royal brother has
gone to such great lengths

319
00:22:33,185 --> 00:22:34,720
just to use you to threaten me,

320
00:22:35,620 --> 00:22:36,988
forcing me to garrison the border.

321
00:22:37,889 --> 00:22:38,889
In three days,

322
00:22:39,491 --> 00:22:41,171
Father will call us to the imperial study.

323
00:22:41,626 --> 00:22:42,626
At that time,

324
00:22:43,095 --> 00:22:44,496
he will definitely confront me.

325
00:22:44,563 --> 00:22:46,083
I'll take care of the Yin Zhou matter,

326
00:22:46,565 --> 00:22:47,399
but the border issue

327
00:22:47,400 --> 00:22:49,240
must not be agreed to
under any circumstances.

328
00:22:49,601 --> 00:22:50,768
These painstaking efforts

329
00:22:50,769 --> 00:22:52,329
to form factions and engage in cronyism

330
00:22:52,437 --> 00:22:54,077
should never have been undertaken by you.

331
00:22:54,406 --> 00:22:55,507
And believe me,

332
00:22:55,874 --> 00:22:57,142
I already have a foolproof plan

333
00:22:57,442 --> 00:22:58,882
to ensure our safety for a lifetime.

334
00:22:59,030 --> 00:23:01,157
As long as you do nothing.

335
00:23:05,784 --> 00:23:06,784
Since

336
00:23:07,185 --> 00:23:08,520
we can't persuade each other,

337
00:23:09,221 --> 00:23:10,221
then

338
00:23:10,355 --> 00:23:11,622
I'll have to use my own methods

339
00:23:11,623 --> 00:23:12,623
to protect you.

340
00:23:14,793 --> 00:23:15,793
A Qi!

341
00:23:16,194 --> 00:23:17,194
A Qi!

342
00:23:19,164 --> 00:23:20,164
A Qi!

343
00:23:21,833 --> 00:23:22,833
A Qi!

344
00:23:24,803 --> 00:23:25,203
A Qi!

345
00:23:25,670 --> 00:23:27,048
What on earth are you trying to do?

346
00:23:27,072 --> 00:23:28,273
Your so-called foolproof plan

347
00:23:28,940 --> 00:23:32,684
is for you to do dangerous things
yourself while I live on like a fool.

348
00:23:33,345 --> 00:23:35,256
Rather than let you go
down an irreversible path,

349
00:23:35,280 --> 00:23:35,814
it's better

350
00:23:36,148 --> 00:23:37,315
to keep you in Yunhe Palace

351
00:23:37,816 --> 00:23:38,816
at least

352
00:23:38,917 --> 00:23:39,917
it can save your life.

353
00:23:40,218 --> 00:23:41,286
Yin Zhou is insane.

354
00:23:42,087 --> 00:23:43,221
You're no match for him.

355
00:23:43,555 --> 00:23:44,022
A Qi,

356
00:23:44,375 --> 00:23:46,725
When I succeed, we can travel
anywhere in the world, living freely,

357
00:23:46,726 --> 00:23:47,925
leading the life you've always wanted.

358
00:23:47,926 --> 00:23:48,927
Isn't that wonderful?

359
00:23:49,086 --> 00:23:49,620
Why-

360
00:23:49,661 --> 00:23:50,661
If...

361
00:23:51,930 --> 00:23:52,930
you fail,

362
00:23:56,334 --> 00:23:58,334
what's the point of me
living alone in this world?

363
00:23:59,571 --> 00:24:00,691
What meaning would there be?

364
00:24:03,255 --> 00:24:04,255
A Qi!

365
00:24:05,143 --> 00:24:05,744
A Qi!

366
00:24:05,769 --> 00:24:06,769
Guards!

367
00:24:07,078 --> 00:24:08,423
Guard the young lord day and night.

368
00:24:08,447 --> 00:24:09,447
Without my permission,

369
00:24:09,748 --> 00:24:11,068
no one is allowed to let him out.

370
00:24:11,249 --> 00:24:11,450
Yes, Your Highness.

371
00:24:11,683 --> 00:24:11,983
Your Highness,

372
00:24:11,983 --> 00:24:12,983
A Qi!

373
00:24:17,589 --> 00:24:18,223
Your Highness,

374
00:24:18,590 --> 00:24:19,590
It's my incompetence.

375
00:24:19,991 --> 00:24:20,492
In the past two days,

376
00:24:20,819 --> 00:24:22,770
I failed to find any evidence
against the Crown Prince.

377
00:24:22,794 --> 00:24:25,907
His cronies are just indulging in
eating, drinking, whoring, and gambling.

378
00:24:25,931 --> 00:24:27,411
Even if I report them to His Majesty,

379
00:24:27,566 --> 00:24:28,566
I'm afraid

380
00:24:29,167 --> 00:24:30,902
it won't harm them in the slightest.

381
00:24:31,361 --> 00:24:32,681
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

382
00:24:33,438 --> 00:24:35,598
Although Yin Zhou is usually
arrogant and overbearing,

383
00:24:36,007 --> 00:24:37,375
when it comes to crucial matters,

384
00:24:37,642 --> 00:24:39,044
he is extremely cautious.

385
00:24:39,517 --> 00:24:42,320
Of course it's not easy to
find evidence against him.

386
00:24:43,287 --> 00:24:44,287
Your Highness,

387
00:24:44,482 --> 00:24:46,985
The Crown Prince is known
for his enjoyment of male company,

388
00:24:47,018 --> 00:24:48,820
and is always surrounded by young men.

389
00:24:49,354 --> 00:24:50,288
But after all this time,

390
00:24:50,289 --> 00:24:51,729
I'm sure His Majesty is aware of it.

391
00:24:51,857 --> 00:24:52,857
But

392
00:24:53,124 --> 00:24:54,764
that's not really evidence of wrongdoing.

393
00:24:54,807 --> 00:24:55,807
Wait a minute.

394
00:24:56,475 --> 00:24:58,235
Isn't there a seductive
and fragile young man

395
00:24:58,396 --> 00:25:00,699
around Yin Zhou,

396
00:25:00,799 --> 00:25:02,467
with eyes as enchanting as silk?

397
00:25:03,702 --> 00:25:04,702
In the past,

398
00:25:04,769 --> 00:25:06,609
I think I have seen
him at the hunting grounds.

399
00:25:08,206 --> 00:25:10,041
Has Your Highness never heard that

400
00:25:10,308 --> 00:25:11,519
everyone at our Yunshang Pavilion

401
00:25:11,543 --> 00:25:13,245
is a master at performing?

402
00:25:15,747 --> 00:25:16,348
Your Highness,

403
00:25:16,648 --> 00:25:18,728
That young man is just a
performer selling his body.

404
00:25:18,783 --> 00:25:20,986
He's probably insignificant
to the Crown Prince.

405
00:25:21,453 --> 00:25:23,688
If you want to threaten
him with this man's life,

406
00:25:23,955 --> 00:25:24,489
I'm afraid...

407
00:25:24,890 --> 00:25:26,050
He's certainly not important,

408
00:25:26,258 --> 00:25:28,059
but the Yunshang Pavilion behind him...

409
00:25:31,383 --> 00:25:32,851
What does Your Highness mean?

410
00:25:33,465 --> 00:25:35,943
The Empress and Yin Zhou have been
entrenched in the court for a long time.

411
00:25:35,967 --> 00:25:37,445
To maintain their
relationships all over,

412
00:25:37,469 --> 00:25:38,737
they must need a lot of money.

413
00:25:39,604 --> 00:25:41,273
If it weren't their own business,

414
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:42,941
Yin Zhou wouldn't trust

415
00:25:42,974 --> 00:25:44,252
the people from Yunshang Pavilion so much

416
00:25:44,276 --> 00:25:45,716
and even bring them into the palace.

417
00:25:46,611 --> 00:25:48,647
The hidden beneficiary of Yunshang Pavilion

418
00:25:49,281 --> 00:25:50,615
might very well be Yin Zhou.

419
00:25:51,883 --> 00:25:52,917
I'll go investigate right away.

420
00:25:52,918 --> 00:25:53,918
Wait a minute.

421
00:25:54,152 --> 00:25:55,152
Your Highness,

422
00:25:55,253 --> 00:25:56,731
Just because that performer
is from Yunshang Pavilion

423
00:25:56,755 --> 00:25:57,789
is not enough evidence

424
00:25:57,856 --> 00:25:59,124
to make such a judgment.

425
00:25:59,457 --> 00:26:02,057
Even if Yunshang Pavilion is the
Crown Prince's private property,

426
00:26:02,527 --> 00:26:03,761
if we go there rashly,

427
00:26:03,762 --> 00:26:04,963
we will definitely alert them.

428
00:26:06,731 --> 00:26:08,342
We need to investigate Yunshang Pavilion,

429
00:26:08,366 --> 00:26:10,035
but not openly.

430
00:26:10,535 --> 00:26:11,736
Find a way

431
00:26:12,070 --> 00:26:13,270
to get the account books back.

432
00:26:13,772 --> 00:26:15,507
If they really have financial transactions,

433
00:26:15,974 --> 00:26:17,275
there must be records.

434
00:26:18,476 --> 00:26:19,836
I accept the order, Your Highness.

435
00:26:39,965 --> 00:26:40,965
Your Highness,

436
00:26:42,734 --> 00:26:43,734
Sit down.

437
00:26:43,802 --> 00:26:44,802
Well?

438
00:26:45,136 --> 00:26:46,136
It's my incompetence.

439
00:26:46,237 --> 00:26:47,597
I failed to get the account books.

440
00:26:47,772 --> 00:26:48,772
What happened?

441
00:26:49,240 --> 00:26:50,600
Your Highness's guess was correct.

442
00:26:50,775 --> 00:26:52,653
There is indeed something
fishy about Yunshang Pavilion.

443
00:26:52,677 --> 00:26:54,279
When the three of us arrived,

444
00:26:54,379 --> 00:26:55,779
Yunshang Pavilion appeared
normal on the surface,

445
00:26:55,780 --> 00:26:57,140
with no signs of anything unusual.

446
00:26:57,716 --> 00:26:58,049
But

447
00:26:58,650 --> 00:26:59,994
when we tried to get the account books,

448
00:27:00,018 --> 00:27:02,887
the manager had disappeared
with the account books.

449
00:27:03,855 --> 00:27:05,323
Duan Yi and Ziming

450
00:27:05,757 --> 00:27:06,757
were even injured.

451
00:27:08,960 --> 00:27:10,240
Please punish me, Your Highness.

452
00:27:13,632 --> 00:27:14,632
Forget it.

453
00:27:15,800 --> 00:27:16,901
Let them rest and recover.

454
00:27:17,769 --> 00:27:18,769
Today's matter...

455
00:27:19,004 --> 00:27:20,724
Although we failed to catch them red-handed

456
00:27:20,939 --> 00:27:22,316
It's still good to let Yin Zhou know

457
00:27:22,340 --> 00:27:23,874
that I've found out

458
00:27:23,875 --> 00:27:24,875
about his private assets

459
00:27:25,143 --> 00:27:26,143
Yes.

460
00:27:27,178 --> 00:27:28,178
Your Highness...

461
00:27:30,054 --> 00:27:32,342
This is all we found at
the Yunshang Pavillion.

462
00:27:43,019 --> 00:27:44,259
Your Highness the Crown Prince,

463
00:27:44,418 --> 00:27:46,931
The Fifth Prince somehow
found out about Yunshang Pavillion.

464
00:27:47,999 --> 00:27:49,343
Fortunately, that person was clever

465
00:27:49,367 --> 00:27:52,103
and didn't let him get the
account books or other evidence

466
00:27:52,971 --> 00:27:55,273
He's actually started
investigating my private assets

467
00:27:57,008 --> 00:28:00,461
Isn't this the same as trying to
snatch my position as Crown Prince?

468
00:28:00,979 --> 00:28:01,979
Give the order

469
00:28:03,014 --> 00:28:06,284
to fully deal with everyone
inside the Yunshang Pavillion.

470
00:28:07,485 --> 00:28:08,485
Yes

471
00:28:11,956 --> 00:28:13,158
Yin Qi

472
00:28:14,392 --> 00:28:16,728
Let's see what you can use to fight me

473
00:28:22,400 --> 00:28:26,404
I've discussed this matter
with several ministers

474
00:28:28,073 --> 00:28:31,142
They all strongly agree with Qi’s idea.

475
00:28:31,676 --> 00:28:33,945
Now, we just need to determine

476
00:28:33,970 --> 00:28:36,586
who to send to guard the border

477
00:28:41,252 --> 00:28:42,353
Father is wise.

478
00:28:42,667 --> 00:28:43,734
I think

479
00:28:44,055 --> 00:28:46,524
that the Fifth Royal Brother
has such profound insights

480
00:28:46,591 --> 00:28:49,227
and would be perfect as a border general

481
00:28:49,627 --> 00:28:52,063
Is Royal Brother treating
border defense as a joke?

482
00:28:52,831 --> 00:28:54,732
Father knows me well

483
00:28:54,766 --> 00:28:56,326
I'm used to writing and reciting poetry

484
00:28:56,634 --> 00:28:58,436
and am not good at
wielding swords and guns.

485
00:28:59,204 --> 00:29:00,364
Leading troops into battle...

486
00:29:02,474 --> 00:29:03,834
is something I know nothing about.

487
00:29:04,476 --> 00:29:05,836
Fifth Brother is being too modest.

488
00:29:06,277 --> 00:29:08,279
Back then, for the matter of Concubine Chen

489
00:29:08,573 --> 00:29:10,375
you even fought with me.

490
00:29:10,448 --> 00:29:12,483
It didn't seem like you were unskilled then

491
00:29:12,484 --> 00:29:13,484
Enough!

492
00:29:13,667 --> 00:29:16,521
I summoned you here
to discuss the border matter,

493
00:29:16,688 --> 00:29:18,623
not to watch you two brothers bicker!

494
00:29:19,257 --> 00:29:21,258
You're not thinking about
how to share my worries

495
00:29:21,259 --> 00:29:22,694
but are just quibbling.

496
00:29:23,061 --> 00:29:24,762
How can I rely on you?

497
00:29:25,930 --> 00:29:26,431
Father

498
00:29:26,765 --> 00:29:28,099
This isn't my fault

499
00:29:28,767 --> 00:29:29,734
Fifth Brother proposed it himself

500
00:29:29,735 --> 00:29:31,179
to send someone to reorganize the border

501
00:29:31,203 --> 00:29:32,705
but now he's refusing to go.

502
00:29:33,615 --> 00:29:34,615
Could it be...

503
00:29:36,040 --> 00:29:37,960
that he's been influenced
by the foreign prince?

504
00:29:40,211 --> 00:29:42,514
I've heard that Pei Yanzhi
is outside the palace

505
00:29:42,539 --> 00:29:43,539
It doesn't matter

506
00:29:44,082 --> 00:29:46,918
What trouble can a hostage cause?

507
00:29:48,253 --> 00:29:49,253
Father,

508
00:29:49,641 --> 00:29:52,600
Yanzhi usually likes to go out of
the palace to drink and have fun

509
00:29:52,624 --> 00:29:54,926
This is indeed my fault for
neglecting to discipline him

510
00:29:55,326 --> 00:29:58,983
I always thought Yanzhi was
just a hostage so I let him be.

511
00:30:00,565 --> 00:30:01,565
I've heard

512
00:30:02,200 --> 00:30:02,834
that Yanzhi usually

513
00:30:02,835 --> 00:30:04,034
likes to go to a place

514
00:30:04,035 --> 00:30:05,670
called Yunshang Pavilion

515
00:30:13,578 --> 00:30:14,611
I wonder if Crown Brother

516
00:30:14,612 --> 00:30:16,147
has heard something

517
00:30:16,614 --> 00:30:19,017
and thus has a
misunderstanding about Yanzhi

518
00:30:23,855 --> 00:30:24,855
Alright

519
00:30:25,290 --> 00:30:26,410
Regarding the border matter,

520
00:30:26,831 --> 00:30:27,999
let me think about it more.

521
00:30:30,146 --> 00:30:31,180
You may all leave.

522
00:30:32,530 --> 00:30:33,530
Yes

523
00:30:33,598 --> 00:30:34,598
Yes, Father

524
00:30:48,913 --> 00:30:50,433
Do you think finding Yunshang Pavilion

525
00:30:50,515 --> 00:30:51,715
means you have the upper hand?

526
00:30:51,983 --> 00:30:53,327
You can protect Pei Yanzhi for a while

527
00:30:53,351 --> 00:30:54,711
but you can't protect him forever!

528
00:30:55,773 --> 00:30:57,675
If you dare to oppose me again

529
00:30:58,449 --> 00:31:00,718
you'll be collecting your prince's body.

530
00:31:02,894 --> 00:31:04,863
Instead of boasting here, Crown Brother,

531
00:31:07,131 --> 00:31:08,499
you should think about

532
00:31:09,267 --> 00:31:10,267
how to hide

533
00:31:10,335 --> 00:31:12,036
your shameful deeds

534
00:31:14,805 --> 00:31:16,206
You probably don't know yet

535
00:31:17,008 --> 00:31:19,277
that Pei Yanzhi has long been my man.

536
00:31:20,538 --> 00:31:26,711
He obeys my every command obediently, like
a dog wagging its tail and begging for mercy

537
00:31:29,654 --> 00:31:30,654
I understand Yanzhi.

538
00:31:31,055 --> 00:31:32,815
He wouldn't associate
with someone like you.

539
00:31:33,591 --> 00:31:35,994
What have you done to him?

540
00:32:14,866 --> 00:32:16,106
Why are you drinking like this?

541
00:32:20,171 --> 00:32:21,372
It's the Mid-Autumn Festival again

542
00:32:22,941 --> 00:32:23,941
In the past

543
00:32:25,076 --> 00:32:26,210
every Mid-Autumn night

544
00:32:26,844 --> 00:32:28,844
we would go to Zhou
Bridge to release sky lanterns

545
00:32:29,781 --> 00:32:30,782
But this year

546
00:32:31,950 --> 00:32:33,251
even if you make sky lanterns

547
00:32:34,352 --> 00:32:36,187
I won't let you leave this room.

548
00:32:39,290 --> 00:32:40,792
Even if I can't leave this room,

549
00:32:41,712 --> 00:32:43,752
the guards outside will
release the lanterns for me

550
00:32:46,130 --> 00:32:47,570
to pray for the Concubine's blessing

551
00:32:53,604 --> 00:32:55,324
Since you chose to stand by Yin Zhou's side

552
00:32:55,740 --> 00:32:57,208
why are you treating me so well?

553
00:32:57,442 --> 00:32:58,442
Why?

554
00:32:58,643 --> 00:33:00,725
Making me foolishly believe
in you for so many years

555
00:33:01,045 --> 00:33:02,880
only to find out in the end

556
00:33:03,681 --> 00:33:05,883
that all of this was just a lie...

557
00:33:07,218 --> 00:33:08,218
Why?

558
00:33:08,853 --> 00:33:09,853
A Qi

559
00:33:10,788 --> 00:33:11,788
What's wrong with you?

560
00:33:12,190 --> 00:33:13,524
What are you talking about?

561
00:33:13,991 --> 00:33:15,026
What's wrong with me?

562
00:33:15,960 --> 00:33:17,595
I really can't do anything about you

563
00:33:17,855 --> 00:33:19,190
I know I should hate you,

564
00:33:20,331 --> 00:33:21,331
blame you...

565
00:33:23,000 --> 00:33:24,202
But compared to hatred

566
00:33:24,869 --> 00:33:27,305
I care more about your life.

567
00:33:28,473 --> 00:33:29,741
I also hate myself.

568
00:33:31,009 --> 00:33:35,413
Why can Yin Zhou
threaten me with your life...

569
00:33:38,983 --> 00:33:42,687
and the only way I can
protect you is to lock you up?

570
00:33:43,788 --> 00:33:44,788
Yin Zhou

571
00:33:45,390 --> 00:33:46,624
What did he say to you?

572
00:33:47,158 --> 00:33:48,960
You probably don't know yet

573
00:33:49,460 --> 00:33:52,129
that Pei Yanzhi has long been my man

574
00:33:52,130 --> 00:33:53,130
Yanzhi

575
00:33:54,932 --> 00:33:56,000
You're mine

576
00:34:04,642 --> 00:34:05,643
You're crazy

577
00:34:06,044 --> 00:34:07,844
Even if I am, it's
because you drove me to it

578
00:34:13,751 --> 00:34:14,751
Yanzhi

579
00:34:16,254 --> 00:34:17,254
Did you ever

580
00:34:19,690 --> 00:34:21,359
have genuine feelings for me?

581
00:34:33,805 --> 00:34:34,805
A Qi

582
00:34:37,809 --> 00:34:38,809
A Qi,

583
00:34:54,025 --> 00:34:55,025
For you,

584
00:34:56,394 --> 00:34:57,634
my sincerity is unquestionable.

585
00:34:59,363 --> 00:35:00,363
In this life,

586
00:35:01,866 --> 00:35:04,135
I do not seek to be with
you side by side forever.

587
00:35:05,570 --> 00:35:06,570
I only wish

588
00:35:07,572 --> 00:35:08,932
to cut through the thorns for you,

589
00:35:11,275 --> 00:35:12,275
so that you

590
00:35:13,978 --> 00:35:15,847
may have a smooth path to walk on.

591
00:35:17,882 --> 00:35:19,484
Even if I die, I will have no regrets.

592
00:35:21,819 --> 00:35:22,819
A Qi,

593
00:35:25,857 --> 00:35:27,225
Why don't you ever understand me?

594
00:35:45,776 --> 00:35:46,776
Your Highness,

595
00:35:47,445 --> 00:35:49,365
Spare me, Your Royal
Highness, the Crown Prince!

596
00:35:49,814 --> 00:35:50,814
This servant,

597
00:35:51,082 --> 00:35:52,159
this servant and the Fifth Prince

598
00:35:52,183 --> 00:35:53,918
only met briefly during

599
00:35:53,951 --> 00:35:55,553
the autumn hunt a year ago.

600
00:35:56,487 --> 00:35:57,487
This servant,

601
00:35:58,389 --> 00:36:01,259
this servant hasn't said anything.

602
00:36:02,193 --> 00:36:03,995
If it weren't for your incompetence,

603
00:36:04,462 --> 00:36:06,702
how could Yin Qi have found
out about Yunshang Pavilion?

604
00:36:14,338 --> 00:36:15,338
Your Highness,

605
00:36:15,673 --> 00:36:16,673
He's here.

606
00:36:19,043 --> 00:36:20,344
Get him out of here.

607
00:36:20,878 --> 00:36:21,878
Yes, sir.

608
00:36:47,939 --> 00:36:49,574
Why are you so late?

609
00:37:20,871 --> 00:37:22,772
Compared to Your Highness,

610
00:37:22,773 --> 00:37:23,874
Yin Qi is far inferior.

611
00:37:24,642 --> 00:37:27,043
Why get angry over such a person?

612
00:37:27,044 --> 00:37:30,047
Take care not to harm your health.

613
00:37:32,024 --> 00:37:34,360
Didn't you report back that

614
00:37:34,385 --> 00:37:36,621
Yin Qi had never obtained any evidence?

615
00:37:37,321 --> 00:37:39,623
But today in the imperial study,

616
00:37:39,624 --> 00:37:42,627
he threatened me with the
private seal of Yunshang Pavilion.

617
00:37:44,128 --> 00:37:45,795
That day at Yunshang Pavilion,

618
00:37:45,796 --> 00:37:47,664
to avoid arousing suspicion
from Duan Yong and Duan Yi,

619
00:37:47,665 --> 00:37:50,668
this subordinate had to fight with
the people from Yunshang Pavilion.

620
00:37:50,835 --> 00:37:52,737
In the midst of the fight,

621
00:37:53,037 --> 00:37:54,037
perhaps

622
00:37:54,105 --> 00:37:55,939
Duan Yong saw the private seal

623
00:37:55,940 --> 00:37:58,009
and secretly brought it back to the palace.

624
00:37:58,609 --> 00:38:00,177
It is this subordinate's incompetence.

625
00:38:01,479 --> 00:38:02,546
Forget it.

626
00:38:03,026 --> 00:38:04,895
It's just Yunshang Pavilion.

627
00:38:06,483 --> 00:38:09,019
Has Yin Qi become suspicious of you?

628
00:38:09,453 --> 00:38:11,054
In this subordinate's opinion,

629
00:38:11,195 --> 00:38:13,264
he should know nothing.

630
00:38:14,125 --> 00:38:16,926
Otherwise, he wouldn't
be floundering around

631
00:38:16,927 --> 00:38:19,063
like a headless fly,

632
00:38:19,397 --> 00:38:20,331
However,

633
00:38:20,332 --> 00:38:22,033
this subordinate can confirm that

634
00:38:22,633 --> 00:38:23,968
everything he does

635
00:38:24,802 --> 00:38:26,069
is to protect

636
00:38:26,070 --> 00:38:27,104
Pei Yanzhi.

637
00:38:29,226 --> 00:38:30,828
This matter with Yunshang Pavillion,

638
00:38:31,275 --> 00:38:32,843
[they way it turned
out] is all thanks to you.

639
00:38:33,277 --> 00:38:37,981
If he had obtained the accounts,
I would be in great trouble.

640
00:38:37,982 --> 00:38:39,684
This subordinate asks for nothing else,

641
00:38:40,017 --> 00:38:41,217
only that Your Highness

642
00:38:41,218 --> 00:38:42,653
may achieve your wishes.

643
00:38:46,490 --> 00:38:51,095
It would be best if we could
eliminate Yin Qi quietly.

644
00:38:51,562 --> 00:38:53,063
For so many years,

645
00:38:53,064 --> 00:38:55,265
Father has been promising Mother

646
00:38:55,266 --> 00:38:57,368
to make me the Crown Prince.

647
00:38:57,735 --> 00:38:59,937
Actually, this princess knows

648
00:39:00,104 --> 00:39:03,606
that Father just wants us brothers
to compete with each other,

649
00:39:03,607 --> 00:39:05,643
to maintain a balance of power.

650
00:39:06,043 --> 00:39:08,512
Your Highness has worked
tirelessly for the court,

651
00:39:08,946 --> 00:39:11,047
how can the Emperor treat you like this?

652
00:39:11,048 --> 00:39:13,017
Born into the imperial family,

653
00:39:13,384 --> 00:39:15,219
isn't it just like this?

654
00:39:15,753 --> 00:39:17,687
Today you surpass me,

655
00:39:17,688 --> 00:39:19,757
tomorrow I will be stronger than you.

656
00:39:20,124 --> 00:39:21,691
I just didn't expect

657
00:39:21,692 --> 00:39:23,728
that the insignificant Fifth Brother

658
00:39:23,894 --> 00:39:26,997
would now become my rival.

659
00:40:10,941 --> 00:40:11,941
It seems

660
00:40:12,309 --> 00:40:13,676
that we still need to find a way

661
00:40:13,677 --> 00:40:14,845
to make Yanzhi speak up.

662
00:40:16,080 --> 00:40:17,800
Otherwise, keeping him imprisoned like this

663
00:40:18,048 --> 00:40:19,450
isn't a long-term solution at all.

664
00:40:22,753 --> 00:40:23,753
Brother,

665
00:40:26,190 --> 00:40:27,190
what is it,

666
00:40:27,324 --> 00:40:28,524
going out of the palace again?

667
00:40:28,826 --> 00:40:30,327
Tonight is the Mid-Autumn Festival,

668
00:40:30,352 --> 00:40:31,963
and the lantern festival
outside is very lively.

669
00:40:32,096 --> 00:40:33,497
I have already reported to Father,

670
00:40:33,597 --> 00:40:36,345
and today he has specially allowed me
to take Granny Su out of the palace with me.

671
00:40:40,371 --> 00:40:41,371
Brother,

672
00:40:41,672 --> 00:40:43,832
you've been keeping Yanzhi
locked up for several days.

673
00:40:44,041 --> 00:40:45,309
What is your intention really?

674
00:40:46,510 --> 00:40:47,745
Are you angry with him,

675
00:40:48,679 --> 00:40:50,079
or is it because of something else?

676
00:40:51,682 --> 00:40:52,842
I consider him one of my own,

677
00:40:53,784 --> 00:40:55,252
yet he refuses to tell me anything.

678
00:40:56,854 --> 00:40:57,854
If I don't lock him up,

679
00:40:58,255 --> 00:41:00,090
who knows what he might do outside?

680
00:41:00,724 --> 00:41:02,359
If Father finds out,

681
00:41:03,194 --> 00:41:04,434
I won't be able to protect him.

682
00:41:06,397 --> 00:41:07,531
I think

683
00:41:07,965 --> 00:41:09,633
that continuing like this

684
00:41:10,167 --> 00:41:10,801
won't solve anything.

685
00:41:11,101 --> 00:41:12,301
It's bad for both you and him.

686
00:41:12,870 --> 00:41:14,190
Why not take advantage of tonight

687
00:41:14,305 --> 00:41:15,816
to go and release sky lanterns together

688
00:41:15,840 --> 00:41:16,840
and clear the air?

689
00:41:17,041 --> 00:41:18,881
It would be much better
to be open and honest.

690
00:41:19,176 --> 00:41:20,276
Keeping him locked up now

691
00:41:20,277 --> 00:41:21,679
at least ensures his safety.

692
00:41:22,046 --> 00:41:23,113
If he's released,

693
00:41:25,049 --> 00:41:27,351
Forget it, don't get involved.

694
00:41:28,452 --> 00:41:29,452
Oh,

695
00:41:29,653 --> 00:41:32,013
take Duan Yi and Duan Yong
to escort you out of the palace.

696
00:41:33,891 --> 00:41:35,491
Don't get involved in my affairs either.

697
00:41:40,731 --> 00:41:41,899
Heshu, rest assured,

698
00:41:42,433 --> 00:41:44,845
your brother will definitely
change the outcome of the past life.

699
00:41:44,869 --> 00:41:47,037
And let you live a carefree life forever.

700
00:41:50,741 --> 00:41:51,942
Look at this,

701
00:41:53,377 --> 00:41:54,411
it's so interesting.

702
00:41:54,612 --> 00:41:55,846
Give me one of these.

703
00:41:56,947 --> 00:41:58,616
Take a look, choose whatever you like.

704
00:42:00,284 --> 00:42:01,552
What would you like, sir?

705
00:42:02,219 --> 00:42:03,486
Selling medicine?

706
00:42:03,487 --> 00:42:04,054
Don't worry,

707
00:42:04,055 --> 00:42:05,288
fresh flowers.

708
00:42:05,289 --> 00:42:06,609
Take a look at the fresh flowers.

709
00:42:07,224 --> 00:42:07,992
They look great.

710
00:42:07,992 --> 00:42:08,992
You have excellent taste.

711
00:42:09,760 --> 00:42:10,594
Thank you, young master.

712
00:42:10,594 --> 00:42:11,462
I want this one.

713
00:42:11,462 --> 00:42:12,462
Take two of them.

714
00:42:12,630 --> 00:42:13,630
Really.

715
00:42:14,265 --> 00:42:15,465
Okay, I'll wrap them up for you.

716
00:42:15,466 --> 00:42:16,666
The feel is really nice.

717
00:42:16,667 --> 00:42:18,068
Does this look good on me?

718
00:42:18,502 --> 00:42:19,637
This one fits too.

719
00:42:19,937 --> 00:42:21,572
Take a look.

720
00:42:26,644 --> 00:42:27,644
Heshu

721
00:42:28,379 --> 00:42:29,379
Heshu

722
00:42:30,781 --> 00:42:31,781
Is that you, Heshu?

723
00:42:32,829 --> 00:42:33,829
Brother Yanzhi...

724
00:42:34,764 --> 00:42:35,764
Heshu...

725
00:42:36,053 --> 00:42:37,063
tonight is the Mid-Autumn Festival.

726
00:42:37,087 --> 00:42:38,732
I want to go out of the palace for a while.

727
00:42:38,757 --> 00:42:39,757
Can you...

728
00:42:39,917 --> 00:42:42,678
You want to go out of the palace
to fly sky lanterns with my brother?

729
00:42:42,793 --> 00:42:43,793
That's right

730
00:42:44,094 --> 00:42:45,094
Leave it to me

731
00:42:52,469 --> 00:42:53,469
Sixth Princess

732
00:42:54,772 --> 00:42:55,772
My brother said

733
00:42:56,073 --> 00:42:57,808
You two have worked hard on duty

734
00:42:57,975 --> 00:42:59,910
You can take a rest tonight

735
00:43:01,045 --> 00:43:02,045
Sixth Princess

736
00:43:02,212 --> 00:43:03,446
Even if the prince wants
to convey a message

737
00:43:03,447 --> 00:43:04,548
He would send Sergeant Duan

738
00:43:04,982 --> 00:43:06,450
Why would he trouble you?

739
00:43:07,561 --> 00:43:08,395
Do you know?

740
00:43:08,420 --> 00:43:10,019
The person locked up
here is a young noble!

741
00:43:10,020 --> 00:43:11,055
Of noble status!

742
00:43:12,122 --> 00:43:14,391
My imperial brother asked
me to convey the message.

743
00:43:14,425 --> 00:43:15,459
It's perfectly normal

744
00:43:18,963 --> 00:43:19,963
Go now, go now

745
00:43:29,673 --> 00:43:32,252
When this princess takes action,
there's nothing that can't be accomplished.

746
00:43:32,276 --> 00:43:33,677
Thank you, Heshu

747
00:43:39,583 --> 00:43:42,452
You've been silent all for all these
days since my brother locked you up.

748
00:43:42,453 --> 00:43:43,954
He ignores me when I talk to him

749
00:43:45,222 --> 00:43:47,758
I don't care whatever the
unresolved issue between you two is.

750
00:43:47,858 --> 00:43:51,662
You should take advantage of this beautiful
night to reconcile and make up quickly.

751
00:43:56,767 --> 00:43:57,935
This fragrance...

752
00:43:58,335 --> 00:44:00,904
Why is it so similar to the incense
my mother used when she was alive...

753
00:44:01,405 --> 00:44:03,183
I want to pray for the
well-being of Concubine Chen

754
00:44:03,207 --> 00:44:05,585
So I'm using the incense she
loved the most when she was alive

755
00:44:05,609 --> 00:44:09,303
Just for this heartfelt gesture of yours,
my brother will surely be very touched.

756
00:44:15,705 --> 00:44:16,705
Let's go

757
00:44:39,710 --> 00:44:40,710
Who are you?
